OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780341071
OL,3,CPolice name boy who disappeared in
OL,4,Criver in 'every parents' worst
OL,5,Cnightmare'
OL,7,FA boy who disappeared in the River Don
OL,8,Fat the weekend has been named, as
OL,9,Fpolice confirmed there has been no
OL,10,Findication he has survived.
OL,12,FMackenzie Swift was seen entering the
OL,13,Friver in Mexborough late on Saturday,
OL,14,Fwith searches for the 11-year-old
OL,15,Ftoday entering their third day.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780341071
OL,3,CPolice name boy who disappeared in
OL,4,Criver in 'every parents' worst
OL,5,Cnightmare'
OL,7,FBut despite joint efforts alongside
OL,8,Ffire services, mountain rescue and
OL,9,Fambulance crews, South Yorkshire
OL,10,FPolice said there had been no signs he
OL,11,Fhad exited the water and that
OL,12,FMackenzie was unlikely to have
OL,13,Fsurvived in the river for this amount
OL,14,Fof time.
OL,16,FIn an update, the force said they
OL,17,Fcontinued to "do everything we can to
OL,18,Ffind" Mackenzie, but said they had had
OL,19,Fto make the "heartbreaking
OL,20,Fconversation" with his family.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780341071
OL,3,CPolice name boy who disappeared in
OL,4,Criver in 'every parents' worst
OL,5,Cnightmare'
OL,7,FA spokesperson said: "Sadly none of
OL,8,Four enquiries so far have found any
OL,9,Findication that he got out of the
OL,10,Fwater.
OL,12,F"His family are in all of our thoughts
OL,13,Fand prayers, and are being supported
OL,14,Fand kept updated on the progress of
OL,15,Fthe search operation."
OL,17,FThe alarm was raised just after 8pm on
OL,18,FSaturday after Mackenzie had been seen
OL,19,Fentering the river near to Ferry Boat
OL,20,FLane, but was not seen getting out.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780341071
OL,3,CPolice name boy who disappeared in
OL,4,Criver in 'every parents' worst
OL,5,Cnightmare'
OL,7,FIt follows a number of other water-
OL,8,Frelated deaths across the country
OL,9,Famidst a spell of hot weather.
OL,11,FPolice in North Yorkshire confirmed on
OL,12,FSunday night that a 13-year-old girl
OL,13,Fhad died after being recovered fro the
OL,14,FRiver Wharfe at Burnsall, near Skipton.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, teenager Muhammed Secka
OL,17,Fdied after getting into trouble in a
OL,18,Flake at the Rother Valley Country Park
OL,19,Fin South Yorkshire.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780341071
OL,3,CPolice name boy who disappeared in
OL,4,Criver in 'every parents' worst
OL,5,Cnightmare'
OL,7,FDoncaster District Commander, Chief
OL,8,FSuperintendent Pete Thorp, said: "We
OL,9,Fwill continue to do everything in our
OL,10,Fpower to find Mackenzie and to support
OL,11,Fhis family through this incredibly
OL,12,Fdifficult time.
OL,14,F"They truly are living every parent's
OL,15,Fworst nightmare.
OL,26,@pD@bOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780341071
OL,3,CPolice name boy who disappeared in
OL,4,Criver in 'every parents' worst
OL,5,Cnightmare'
OL,7,F"We are utilising a range of
OL,8,Fspecialist resources and organisations
OL,9,Ffrom across the region. Officers will
OL,10,Fremain at the search site tonight and
OL,11,Ffurther operational activity will
OL,12,Fresume at first light tomorrow
OL,13,F(Tuesday) morning.
OL,15,F"I understand members of the public
OL,16,Fare desperate to help, but I must ask
OL,17,Fthat you leave this work to the
OL,18,Fprofessional search teams.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780341071
OL,3,CPolice name boy who disappeared in
OL,4,Criver in 'every parents' worst
OL,5,Cnightmare'
OL,7,F"Please do not put yourselves or
OL,8,Fothers in danger by searching in and
OL,9,Faround water, and if asked to leave by
OL,10,Fofficers, please understand this is
OL,11,Ffor your own safety and to ensure our
OL,12,Fefforts focus solely on finding
OL,13,FMackenzie.
OL,15,F"The thoughts of all those involved in
OL,16,Fthe extensive search operation remain
OL,17,Fwith Mackenzie and his family."
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@_O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
